{"title":"第一线晨曦——给妈妈","authors":["吴建中"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":2,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一线晨曦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——给妈妈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴建中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你天天早起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我还在酣睡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你便象第一线晨曦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄然照进我梦的旷野。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是翠绿的大榕树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄昏的朦胧里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我收住嫩弱的翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你的枝丫上憩息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是微风一缕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"携来远方的花香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带走我满身的汗水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有那劳累后的叹息……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，妈妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我会变作片片白云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻地、轻轻地擦拭你——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心上永恒的春天。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}